#. Tag: title
#: picprograms.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "PIC Programs"
msgstr "PIC programi"

#. Tag: title
#: picprograms.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manipulation"
msgstr "Manipulacija"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you create a FlowCode or a Text document, you'll notice a drop down "
"menu in the toolbar with a rocket icon. From here, you can manipulate your "
"PIC program; changing it to different forms."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite FlowCode ali besedilni dokument, boste v orodni vrstici opazili "
"spustni meni z ikono rakete. Od tu lahko manipulirate s svojim programom "
"PIC; s spreminjanjem v različne oblike."

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Convert to &microbe;</guimenuitem> - This is used only in "
"&flowcode; documents. This is explained further in <xref linkend=\"flowcode"
"\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Pretvori v &microbe;</guimenuitem> - To se uporablja samo v "
"&flowcode; dokumentih. To je podrobneje razloženo v <xref linkend=\"flowcode"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Convert to Assembly</guimenuitem> - This can be used in four "
"contexts. When a &flowcode; document is open, it will output the &flowcode; "
"as assembly instructions. When a &microbe; document is open, it will invoke "
"the <command>microbe</command> program distributed with &ktechlab; to "
"compile the program. Similarly, if a C program is open, it will attempt to "
"compile it via SDCC. When a text document containing PIC hex is open, it "
"will invoke <command>gpdasm</command> to disassemble the hex."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Pretvori v zbirnik</guimenuitem> - To je mogoče uporabiti v "
"štirih kontekstih. Ko je &flowcode; dokument odprt, bo izpisal &flowcode; "
"kot navodila za zbirnik. Ko je &microbe; dokument odprt, bo priklical "
"program <command>microbe</command>, ki se distribuira z &ktechlab; za "
"prevajanje programa. Podobno, če je program C odprt, ga bo poskušal prevesti "
"prek SDCC. Ko je odprt tekstovni dokument, ki vsebuje hex PIC, bo poklical "
"<command>gpdasm</command>, da razstavi hex."

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Convert to Hex</guimenuitem> - This can also be used in four "
"contexts. As with <guimenuitem>Convert to Assembly</guimenuitem>, this can "
"be used with &flowcode;, &microbe; and C documents. It will also be enabled "
"when an assembly document is open to assemble it via <command>gpasm</"
"command>."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Pretvori v hex</guimenuitem> – To je mogoče uporabiti tudi v "
"štirih kontekstih. Tako kot pri <guimenuitem>Pretvori v zbirnik</"
"guimenuitem>, lahko to uporabite z &flowcode;, &microbe; in C dokumenti. "
"Omogočeno bo tudi, ko je dokument zbirnika odprt, ga sestavite prek "
"<command>gpasm</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Upload to PIC</guimenuitem> - This assembles the PIC program "
"currently being edited, and uploads it using the programmer that the user "
"has selected."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prenesi v PIC</guimenuitem> - To sestavi program PIC, ki se "
"trenutno ureja, in ga naloži s programatorjem, ki ga je izbral uporabnik."

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"None of these actions require the current document to be saved - very useful "
"for when a quick program is required. For non-PIC targets, the "
"<guilabel>Output</guilabel> dialog invoked on clicking on one of these "
"actions can either output the result (always text in the above three cases) "
"to a fresh document, or to a file. If the output is saved to file, it also "
"provides options to load the file after creation, and adding the newly "
"created file to the open project (if one is open)."
msgstr ""
"Nobeno od teh dejanj ne zahteva shranjevanja trenutnega dokumenta - zelo "
"uporabno, ko je hitro potreben program. Za cilje, ki niso PIC, lahko "
"pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izhod</guilabel>, ki se prikliče ob kliku enega od "
"teh dejanj, izpiše rezultat (v zgornjih treh primerih vedno besedilo) v nov "
"dokument ali v datoteko. Če je izhod shranjen v datoteko, ponuja tudi "
"možnosti za nalaganje datoteke po ustvarjanju in dodajanje novo ustvarjene "
"datoteke odprtemu projektu (če je odprt)."

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you can make &ktechlab; always use the same view for displaying "
"the outputted content by selecting the option under <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> settings."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko pri &ktechlab; vedno uporabite isti pogled za prikaz "
"izpisane vsebine, tako da izberete možnost pod <guilabel>Splošnimi</"
"guilabel> nastavitvami."

#. Tag: title
#: picprograms.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uploading"
msgstr "Prenašanje"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktechlab; uses third-party programmers to upload programs to PICs. A "
"variety of common programmers come predefined. Others can be added via the "
"<guilabel>Settings</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&ktechlab; uporablja programatorje tretjih oseb za prenašanje programov v "
"PIC. Različni običajni programatorji so vnaprej določeni. Druge lahko dodate "
"prek pogovornega okna <guilabel>Nastavitve</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of ports is obtained from scanning for serial and parallel ports "
"that are readable and writable. Serial ports are looked for in:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam vrat se pridobi s skeniranjem serijskih in vzporednih vrat, ki so "
"berljiva in zapisljiva. Serijska vrata se iščejo v:"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "/dev/ttyS<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"
msgstr "/dev/ttyS<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "/dev/tts/<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"
msgstr "/dev/tts/<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "/dev/ttyUSB<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"
msgstr "/dev/ttyUSB<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "/dev/usb/tts/<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"
msgstr "/dev/usb/tts/<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parallel ports are looked for in:"
msgstr "Vzporedna vrata se iščejo v:"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "/dev/usb/parport<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"
msgstr "/dev/usb/parport<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: picprograms.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "/dev/usb/parports/<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"
msgstr "/dev/usb/parports/<emphasis>[0..7]</emphasis>"
